query: Give me the top 5 players based on 3 pointers avg across all games from the seasons 2003 to 2014
sql:
SELECT
  full_name,
  AVG(three_points_made) AS avg_three_pointers_per_game
FROM
  `bigquery-public-data.ncaa_basketball.mbb_players_games_sr`
WHERE
  season BETWEEN 2003 AND 2014
  AND played = TRUE
GROUP BY
  full_name,
  player_id
ORDER BY
  avg_three_pointers_per_game DESC
LIMIT
  5

query: Give me the top 5 players based on 3 pointers avg across all games from the seasons 2003 to 2014 in the madison venue
sql:
SELECT
  p.full_name,
  AVG(p.three_points_made) AS avg_three_pointers
FROM
  `bigquery-public-data.ncaa_basketball.mbb_players_games_sr` AS p
JOIN
  `bigquery-public-data.ncaa_basketball.mbb_games_sr` AS g
  ON p.game_id = g.game_id
WHERE
  p.season BETWEEN 2003 AND 2014
  AND LOWER(g.venue_name) LIKE '%madison%'
GROUP BY
  p.player_id,
  p.full_name
ORDER BY
  avg_three_pointers DESC
LIMIT
  5;

query: Do a comparison between Jordan Howard and Trevon Bluiett in the seasons 2015 to 2017
sql:
SELECT
  full_name,
  season,
  COUNT(game_id) AS games_played,
  ROUND(AVG(points), 2) AS avg_points,
  ROUND(AVG(rebounds), 2) AS avg_rebounds,
  ROUND(AVG(assists), 2) AS avg_assists,
  ROUND(AVG(steals), 2) AS avg_steals,
  ROUND(AVG(blocks), 2) AS avg_blocks,
  ROUND(SAFE_DIVIDE(SUM(field_goals_made), SUM(field_goals_att)), 3) AS field_goal_pct,
  ROUND(SAFE_DIVIDE(SUM(three_points_made), SUM(three_points_att)), 3) AS three_point_pct,
  ROUND(SAFE_DIVIDE(SUM(free_throws_made), SUM(free_throws_att)), 3) AS free_throw_pct
FROM
  `bigquery-public-data.ncaa_basketball.mbb_players_games_sr`
WHERE
  full_name IN ('Jordan Howard', 'Trevon Bluiett')
  AND season BETWEEN 2015 AND 2017
GROUP BY
  full_name,
  season
ORDER BY
  full_name,
  season

query: compare performance of the top two players in the season 2016 based on 3 pointers scored
sql:
WITH TopPlayers AS (
  SELECT
    player_id
  FROM
    `bigquery-public-data.ncaa_basketball.mbb_players_games_sr`
  WHERE
    season = 2016
    AND played = TRUE
  GROUP BY
    player_id,
    full_name
  ORDER BY
    SUM(three_points_made) DESC
  LIMIT 2
)
SELECT
  p.full_name,
  p.team_name,
  COUNT(p.game_id) AS games_played,
  SUM(p.points) AS total_points,
  SUM(p.three_points_made) AS total_three_pointers_made,
  SUM(p.three_points_att) AS total_three_pointers_attempted,
  SAFE_DIVIDE(SUM(p.three_points_made), SUM(p.three_points_att)) AS three_point_pct,
  SAFE_DIVIDE(SUM(p.field_goals_made), SUM(p.field_goals_att)) AS field_goal_pct,
  SAFE_DIVIDE(SUM(p.free_throws_made), SUM(p.free_throws_att)) AS free_throw_pct,
  SUM(p.rebounds) AS total_rebounds,
  SUM(p.assists) AS total_assists,
  SUM(p.steals) AS total_steals,
  SUM(p.blocks) AS total_blocks
FROM
  `bigquery-public-data.ncaa_basketball.mbb_players_games_sr` AS p
JOIN
  TopPlayers tp
  ON p.player_id = tp.player_id
WHERE
  p.season = 2016
GROUP BY
  p.full_name,
  p.team_name
ORDER BY
  total_three_pointers_made DESC
